from ultralytics import YOLO
import cv2
import os
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import easyocr

# Load yolo model from path
def load_model(model_path):
    return YOLO(model_path)

# Run inference on the image with the selected model
def run_inference(model, image_path):
    return model.predict(source=image_path, save=False)

# Draw a bounding box on the image
def draw_bounding_box(image, box):
    x1, y1, x2, y2 = map(int, box.xyxy[0])
    cv2.rectangle(image, (x1, y1), (x2, y2), (0, 255, 0), 2)
    return (x1, y1, x2, y2)

# Crop the image to the bounding box area
def crop_image(image, box):
    x1, y1, x2, y2 = map(int, box.xyxy[0])
    return image[y1:y2, x1:x2]

# Display the results (original, cropped and processed images)
def display_results(original_image, cropped_image):
    plt.figure(figsize=(18, 7))

    # Original image
    plt.subplot(1, 3, 1)
    plt.title("Original Image")
    plt.imshow(cv2.cvtColor(original_image, cv2.COLOR_BGR2RGB))
    plt.axis('off')

    # Cropped image
    plt.subplot(1, 3, 2)
    plt.title("Cropped")
    plt.imshow(cropped_image)
    plt.axis('off')

    plt.show()

# Paths and model setup
pretrained_path = r"C:/Users/Huijb/OneDrive/Bureaublad/Fontys/Semester 4/Group project/YOLOv8/runs/detect/train6/weights/last.pt"
test_image_path = r"C:\Users\Huijb\OneDrive\Bureaublad\Fontys\Semester 4\Group project\YOLOv8\data\images"

model = load_model(pretrained_path)
results = run_inference(model, test_image_path)

max_images = 5 

processed_images = 0
for i, result in enumerate(results):
    if processed_images >= max_images:
        break 
    
    if len(result.boxes) == 0:
        continue

    original_image = result.orig_img

    for j, box in enumerate(result.boxes):
        # Draw bounding box and crop image
        draw_bounding_box(original_image, box)
        cropped_eartag = crop_image(original_image, box)

        # Display results
        display_results(original_image, cropped_eartag)
        processed_images += 1

        if processed_images >= max_images:
            break
